SELECT mona_accesses.id, mona_purchase_users.email, mona_listings.title, mona_users.name, mona_users.username, mona_listings.payment_type FROM mona_accesses, mona_listings_services, mona_purchase_users, mona_listings, mona_users WHERE mona_accesses.service_id = mona_listings_services.service_id AND mona_listings_services.listing_id = mona_listings.id AND mona_listings.provider_id = mona_users.id AND mona_accesses.purchase_user_id = mona_purchase_users.id AND mona_users.id = 1312

SELECT mona_users.id, 
COUNT(CASE WHEN mona_statistics.event=0 then 1 else null end), 
COUNT(mona_accesses.id) 
FROM mona_accesses, mona_listings_services, mona_listings, mona_users, mona_statistics 
WHERE 
mona_accesses.service_id = mona_listings_services.service_id AND 
mona_listings_services.listing_id = mona_listings.id AND 
mona_listings.provider_id = mona_users.id AND 
mona_users.id = mona_statistics.user_id AND 
mona_user.id = 1312
GROUP BY mona_users.id
